        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Terms & Conditions: Admission E-Ticket(s) must be purchased at least 24 hours before your visit date to Dream Forest Langkawi to allow time for transaction processing. Failure to do so may result in normal admission charges being applied at the venue.Eligibility FREE park admission applies to children aged 2 years and below. Adult Ticket: 16 years old and above Child Ticket: 3 – 15 years old Senior Ticket: 60 years old and above Guests with Disabilities (OKU): Guests holding valid disability certificatesAttraction Access Outside food and drinks are not allowed inside the venue. Dangerous materials and items such as bottles, firecrackers, lasers, and any items that may disturb or inconvenience other guests are prohibited. Flash photography is prohibited inside the venue. Re-entry is not allowed after you leave the venue.Additional Information No requests to change the validity date of purchased tickets will be entertained. Tickets are strictly non-transferable, not for resale, not exchangeable, and non-refundable under any circumstances, including external factors beyond reasonable control (e.g. haze, inclement weather, governmental acts, acts of God, riots, or strikes). Tickets will be void if altered, defaced, or tampered with.Important Notes Please ensure tickets are purchased in advance and comply with all venue rules to avoid any inconvenience during entry."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
